\newlabel{tab:mortality_coefficients}{{11}{45}{Binomial GLMM coefficients for the survival--SOM relationship. The model is $\mathrm {logit}(P_{\mathrm {survival}}) = \beta _0 + \beta _1 \cdot \mathrm {SOM} + u_j$, where $u_j \sim \mathcal {N}(0, \sigma ^2_u)$ is a random intercept for spatial block $j$ (column position in common garden). McFadden pseudo-$R^2$: 0 }{table.caption.27}{}}
